  <name>Ouroboros Mobile</name>
  <summary>Intelligent and autonomous study with encrypted database</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Ouroboros Mobile is a comprehensive tool for students seeking organization and efficiency.
      With support for study cycles, spaced repetition, and a database encrypted with SQLCipher.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Automated study cycles</li>
      <li>Repetitions based on forgetting curves</li>
      <li>Secure database with SQLCipher</li>
      <li>Local synchronization via mDNS</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
